TASK 1 :
# 🧹 Sales Data Cleaning and Preprocessing

## 🎯 Objective
To clean and prepare a raw sales dataset by handling missing values, duplicate entries, and inconsistent formats using Python (Pandas).

## 📁 Dataset Description
- 50 rows × 10 columns (raw and cleaned)


## 🧪 Data Cleaning Steps
- Removed duplicate rows
- Dropped rows with missing dates
- Standardized country names to uppercase
- Converted `Date` column to datetime format
- Renamed columns to lowercase with underscores



